        textArea1.setText("***************************************************************\n******************** USER GUIDE ********************************\n**************** DESPICABLE ME GAME ****************************\n***************************************************************\n\n\nI- Prevention of epilepsy risk\n\nII- Some rules for having fun\t\n\nIII- Preface\t\n\nIV- Install the game\t\n\nV- Start the game\t\n\nVI- Goal of the game\t\n\nVII- Main commands\t\n\nVIII- Main functions of the game\t\n\nIX- Troubleshooting section\t\n  \nX- Frequently Asked Questions\t\n\nXI-  to find further help, and contact details\t\n\n\n\nI- Prevention of epilepsy risk\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nRead before use of video games by yourself or your child.\n\nIn some people, visual stimulation to certain flashing lights or light patterns can trigger an epileptic seizure or loss of consciousness. \nThese symptoms may also be in an individual in medical history or have never suffered from epilepsy.\n\n\nII- Some rules for having fun\t\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n\n \tDo not stand too close to the screen\n \tPreferably play the game on a small screen\n \tAvoid playing when tired or lack of sleep\n \tEnsure that the room is well lit. \n \tRest for 10 to 15 minutes per hour of game.  \n\n\nIII- Preface\t\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nDear player, we are pleased to have you with us for this new adventure!\n\nWe have during several months developed this game for you to have a lot of fun.\nFollow the instructions below to get the most from this new experience that we are offering you.\n\nYou will find in our FAQs answers to your questions. However, do not hesitate to contact us (www.despicablemethegame.fr).\n\nGood luck!\n\n\nIV- Install the game\t\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nIn order to play you don’t have to install anything! Just copy and paste the file on your computer! It’s very easy. \nWe chose to have this kind of installation for you, you can play everywhere on any media you want (Your installation just needs to have a Java kit).\n\n\nV- Start the game\t\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nTo start the game, you just have to double click on the DespicableMeGame.jar file. It will run automatically and you will see our home page. \n\nEnjoy the game!\n\n\nVI- Goal of the game\t\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nThis game was inspired by the movie Despicable me. You will be the younger girl, Agnes. Your objective will be to find the Bad Minion and to cure him. Minions are loyal servants of Gru, and a Bad Minion is one with evil behaviors. They are uncontrollable, and they break and eat everything that they find...\n\nSo, you must cure this Bad Minion with a magic liquid and a syringe that you will take during your game. You will go through some rooms, and find some tools, help some characters, answer some questions… To find him.\n\n\nVII- Main commands\t\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nEnter : Confirm your choice\na..z : is the alphabet\n1..0 : are numbers\n←↑→↓: arrows to move\n\n\nVIII- Main functions of the game\t\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nThe main page, proposes the player to play with Agnes during this game, click on “Next” and start it, or continue it, if the game has already started. \nIf the player wants to leave the game, click on “Exit”. \n  \nThe main page of the game\nDuring the play game, when “next” appears, you can go to the next step. If this button is not on the screen, the player has to play the game. And he can leave the game at any time with “Exit”, the playing game will be saved, and the payer will return to the main menu.\nA system of points has been installed in the game. Agnes starts with 1000 points. If she does bad actions, or if she makes the wrong choices, she will lose some points. On the contrary, if she makes the good choices, she will get points. \n\nDuring your trip, Agnes will meet some characters who will need her. After helping them, they will help her, as, for example giving her some tools that Agnes needs for her trip, and to cure the bad Minion.\nFirstly, the player is able to move the little girl with the mouse to go to different places. The player has to click on “next” (in the right corner) to have the next screen and Agnes should open different doors to go to different places.\nLikewise, the player is able to move, but in this case, only in one place, with arrows on the keyboard to look for some object or button on the map.\n \nExample of a room, to move with arrows\n\tWhen Agnes will choose her way:\nBe careful, finding her way is not an easy matter. The little girl will have some … surprises behind some doors, or on her way. \nBesides some ways are risky…\nSometimes, the player might find general knowledge questions. He will have to answer correctly to questions, to progress through the game.\nAt different times in the game, he will have to choose actions for Agnes. According to the decisions of the player, Agnes will get or lose points… Or things will be much worse…\nThere will be a memory exercise. A sequence will appear during 10 sec, the player will have to remember it, and write it when the sequence will disappear from the screen.\n\n \nIX- Troubleshooting section\t\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nTroubleshooting section: errors/problems and solutions\n\n-\tIf you have the 1.0 version of the game, some “Next” buttons might not work.\no\tThe solution is : download the new 2.0 version on our website : www.despicablemethegame.fr\nChoose the upload version compatible with your computer.\n\n-\tYou might not have images on the screen, but only the script.\no\tThe solution is: restart the game Despicable me. And if after restarting the game, you still don’t have images, you will have to restart your computer.\n\n\n\nX- Frequently Asked Questions \n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n\n•\tCan I access Despicable Me Game in my computer, Mac or smartphone ?\nYes and No. This game can be only played on your computer, or on your Mac. \n\n•\tIs this game free?\nYes, this game is totally free. \n\n•\tCan I quit the game before the goal is attained?\nYou can quit the game before the goal attained, but you can’t save your game. When you quit the game, you have to restart the game since the beginning to play again.\n\n•\tIs there sound during the game?\nNo, in the Despicable me game, there is no sound, there is only a graphical interface. \n\n•\tCan I play with the keyboard?\nYes, to play this game, you can use the keyboard and the mouse. You have to follow the instructions given on the screen.\n\n•\tCan I play with someone else? Or is it a game to play alone?\nThere is only one main character in this game, so you have to play alone.\n\n\n \nXI- Where to find further help, and contact details\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nCustomer service : \n\nFor any technical information about this game, you can call the customer service\n\t\tfrom monday to friday 9:00 am to 6:00 to :\n\n\t\t\t0800 250 654 369 \n\nFollow the latest news about this game!\n\nwww.despicablemethegame.fr\n");
